BlackNova Traders - Readme

BlackNova Traders is a web-based, multi-player space exploration game inspired by the popular BBS game of TradeWars. It is coded using PHP, SQL, and 
Javascript.

Version 0.55 / http://www.blacknova.net

Copyright (C) 2000 Ron Harwood <harwoodr@blacknova.net>, L. Patrick Smallwood <thekabal@gmail.com>

This program is free software; you can redistribute it and/or modify it under 
